                "Somali": "Waa waqti aad u dheer"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "I’m so happy to see you again.",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Waan ku faraxsanahay inaan mar kale ku arko"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "Wow, it’s so good to see you again!",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Wow, waa ku faraxsanahay inaan mar kale ku arko!"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "What have you been up to?",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Maxaad ku mashquulsanayd?"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "I’m doing very well, thank you. And you?",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Waan fiicanahay, mahadsanid. Adiga se?"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "I’m fine, thank you.",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Waan fiicanahay, mahadsanid."
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "Great, thanks. How are you?",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Wanaagsan, mahadsanid. Adiga se?"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "Not bad. You?",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Ma xuma. Adiga se?"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "Couldn’t be better? How about you?",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Iskaba dhaaf. Adiga se?"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Repeat out loud",
            "text": "Wonderful, thank you.",
            "translations": {
                "Somali": "Waa fiican tahay, mahadsanid."
